{
  "stem": "3685.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We didn't like it, because they were confiscating-- they were talking about making collective farms, taking away our land.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We didn't have any business already, but in the meantime, we were working on our land and-- and the whole problem start when the-- when the Germans came in in 1941.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the 22nd of June, the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the 23rd, 10 o'clock in the morning, the Germans were already in our village, because it was 50 kilometers from the border.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And in the first day, we-- we had, right away, bitter experience.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "My sister walked out on the street, and-- and a German car pulled in, pulled down the window when [? she ?]-- and they called her in and spit in her face.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That's an incident I remember, in '41.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She came in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "She was crying.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I says, what happened?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So she says to me, you know what happened?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's what happened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Told me the story, you know, and it really bothered me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I says, I know mine chances are 99% I'll probably not live through.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If I ever live through, I'll-- I'll-- I'll go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It doesn't matter if I get killed or not, I'll go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I lived through, and I went to the Russian army, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I did what I had to do, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[SIGHS] But then, during the Holocaust-- during-- you see, the first-- we-- from June '41 to September '42 we were still-- they kicked us out from our house.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They-- we wanted to-- they gave us a little house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the big house, our house was-- 1/2 of the house was the-- it was like the-- they had the-- what do you call that?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The-- it was the head of the village, you know, the office.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
